Package com.siperian.sif.message Description

Provides data objects and abstract classes for the Siperian Hub APIs. All requests are sub-classes of SiperianRequest.

Send requests to Siperian Hub using SiperianClient.process(com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianRequest), which returns a response that is a sub-class of SiperianResponse.

See Also:
com.siperian.sif.client
